ical elements of an observed active region, such as null points, can be\nreproduced with confidence only by considering the potential-field\napproximation. This study is a preliminary work aiming at understanding the\neffects of electric currents generated by characteristic photospheric motions\non the structure and evolution of the coronal magnetic field.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Jul 2011 13:45:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-28"}
